@node "Starting" "Starting the Control Centre"

Before the program can be started, it would help if it were @{" installed " link "Installation" 0}.

@{b}FROM WORKBENCH@{ub}

Just  double-click the FUBAR_CC icon in the CC directory.  The program will
start.   If  running  from  floppy,  it  can  take  a  few moments to load,
especially on a slow computer.

@{b}FROM SHELL@{ub}

In your Shell window, CD to the CC directory, and type

